%% Diagram: Registration and heartbeat lifecycle
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Service Instance
    participant Reg as Registry
    participant Cli as Client (cached)

    Note over App,Reg: Startup
    App->>Reg: Register {service, host, port, health}
    Reg-->>App: Lease / Session ID

    Note over App,Reg: Steady state
    loop Every heartbeat_interval
        App->>Reg: Heartbeat / KeepAlive
        Reg-->>App: ack
    end
    Reg-->>Cli: Watch event: instance ready
    Cli->>Cli: Update local cache

    Note over App,Reg: Graceful shutdown
    App->>Reg: Deregister
    Reg-->>Cli: Watch event: instance removed
    Cli->>Cli: Drain in-flight, refresh cache

    Note over App,Reg: Crash path (no deregister)
    App--xReg: Heartbeat lost
    Reg->>Reg: Wait sessionTimeout / lease TTL
    Reg-->>Cli: Watch event: instance expired
    Cli->>Cli: Evict from cache
